  "prompt": "Why does my girlfriend of 7 years dont reply to my text or calls when she says that it wont be long. what should I do?",
  "response": "There could be several reasons for her lack of communication:\n\n1. Possible reasons:\n- She might be busy\n- Her phone could be off/battery died\n- She's experiencing personal stress\n- Communication issue\n- Potential relationship problem\n\n2. Recommended actions:\n- Stay calm\n- Send a caring, non-confrontational message\n- Give her reasonable time to respond\n- If pattern continues, have an honest conversation\n- Ask if everything is okay\n\n3. Warning signs to consider:\n- Consistent lack of communication\n- Avoiding direct contact\n- Sudden behavior changes\n\n4. Communication approach:\n- Express your feelings without being accusatory\n- Ask about her well-being\n- Listen to her explanation\n- Discuss communication expectations together\n\n5. If unresolved:\n- Seek relationship counseling\n- Evaluate relationship dynamics\n- Consider personal boundaries\n\nThe key is open, respectful communication and understanding each other's perspectives.\n\nWould you like to discuss this further or need more specific advice about your situation?",
